Package: meetR
Title: Open-Source Group Scheduling with Shiny and Google Sheets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kartik", "Trivedi", email = "kartik0trivedi@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Launch a when2meet-style availability poll directly from R.
    Provide a CSV of proposed dates and hours, authenticate with Google
    Sheets, and meetR creates a shareable Shiny app that collects and
    visualises group availability in real time.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
